    <desc lang="en">Antique shop owner Wu Xie (Xu Zhenxuan) unexpectedly obtains a mysterious silk scroll. His third uncle, Wu Sansheng (Francis Ng), discovers that the scroll contains a hidden map. To find the missing owner of the scroll, Wu Sansheng leads an expedition team consisting of Wu Xie, Pan Zi (Cao Lei), Zhang Qiling (Cheng Xiang), and Da Kui (Ma Jingjing) to explore the locations marked on the map. During their search, Wu Xie meets Wang Pangzi (Sun Gechuanye), who is also exploring the site. Facing various dangers and attacks from mysterious creatures, the team works together, using their wisdom and courage to overcome the perils. Deep underground, they discover a bronze fish with snake-like eyebrows, which unexpectedly uncovers a long-buried past for Wu Sansheng. After meeting with a mysterious woman named A Ning (Li Muchen), Wu Sansheng suddenly disappears. To uncover the truth and find his missing uncle, Wu Xie and his companions embark on a new journey.</desc>
